snippet.title: Ukungu - Early Development Showcase 2023
snippet.description:
Hello all I'm working on a game as the main programmer, you can find all the games updates on our main channel for the game channel, We hope you enjoy this showcase, and we look forward to seeing you in the future!

https://www.youtube.com/@griotwest
https://youtu.be/CKk76PBwm4I

I might post some programming updates or random other project I'm working on here later too

Music:
Original Track - "No Time (Ukungu)"

Written and preformed by
KS The Wolf | https://www.instagram.com/ksthewolf/
Track Composition by
Darius Shipp | https://www.instagram.com/mrshipp/
